The paper deals with facial attribute analysis and face detection, which are both topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for this task suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments conducted on datasets such as CelebA and LFWA suggest that the paper may also be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
